context:
KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;우리는 야심가도, 탐욕가도 아니며 그저 기술을 사랑했던 아해에 불과했지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;We were neither highfliers nor greedy vultures; we were merely children who loved technology.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;처음으로 우리가 숨을 쉰다고 느꼈던 그날을 기억하오?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Do you remember the day when we first felt that we were breathing?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그때는 말일세,&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Back then…&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그 숨만으로도 충분했었소.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;That breath alone would suffice.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;아님 유독…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Or perhaps…&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그날만 공기가 맑았거나.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;It was the air that was exceptionally clear that day.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;그런데 말이야…&gt;
EN:
&lt;By the way…&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;……&gt;

KR:
&lt;…고마워, 파우스트.&gt;
EN:
&lt;…Thank you, Faust.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…황금가지는 대체 어디에 쓰이는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;…So what are Golden Boughs used for, anyway?&gt;

KR:
&lt;생각해 보면 황금가지를 모아오라는 말만 들었지… 그걸 구체적으로 어떻게 하겠다 라는 말은 듣지 못했던 것 같아서.&gt;
EN:
&lt;When I think about it, all we were told was a vague order to collect them… And nothing about what the company plans to do with them.&gt;

KR:
&lt;죽으러 가라는 소리를 우아하게도 말하는군…&gt;
EN:
&lt;That’s one elegant way to tell us to go die a thousand deaths…&gt;
